00:52:47.498 --> 00:52:49.458
Someone is trying to kill us! Please!

520
00:52:49.458 --> 00:52:52.169
They've murdered our friends.
They're after us right now.

521
00:52:52.259 --> 00:52:53.837
<i>I'm having some trouble hearing you.</i>

522
00:52:53.921 --> 00:52:56.104
<i>If you're in the tower.
stay up there. Do you copy?</i>

523
00:52:56.123 --> 00:52:58.843
Yes. yes. we copy! Just hurry.
please! This is an emergency!

524
00:52:58.843 --> 00:53:00.200
- Help me move this. Come on!
- We'll come to you.

525
00:53:00.219 --> 00:53:01.326
<i>- Do you copy?</i>
- Come on!

526
00:53:01.345 --> 00:53:04.204
They're after us!
Someone's been shot!

527
00:53:04.223 --> 00:53:07.684
Our friends have been killed.
and we need help! Please!

528
00:53:07.768 --> 00:53:08.935
Fuck!

529
00:53:35.546 --> 00:53:37.131
What are they doing?

530
00:53:37.631 --> 00:53:39.132
I don't know.

531
00:53:43.137 --> 00:53:45.139
I think they're going down.

532
00:53:46.307 --> 00:53:47.599
Jess.

533
00:54:02.902 --> 00:54:07.369
Hello? Hello? Is anybody
there? Can you hear us? Hello?

534
00:54:37.816 --> 00:54:40.068
Jesus. what are they doing?

535
00:54:40.884 --> 00:54:41.968
We're on fire.

536
00:54:41.987 --> 00:54:43.947
They're trying to burn us out.

537
00:54:46.884 --> 00:54:48.260
Oh. my God.

538
00:54:59.612 --> 00:55:00.756
Carly!

539
00:55:01.757 --> 00:55:02.757
Come here.

540
00:55:02.841 --> 00:55:04.926
Let go of me! Let go!

541
00:55:05.094 --> 00:55:07.845
I'd rather jump than burn to death!

542
00:55:10.683 --> 00:55:12.183
Calm down.

543
00:55:12.267 --> 00:55:13.726
You're right.

544
00:55:13.811 --> 00:55:15.687
- What?
- She's right.

545
00:55:15.729 --> 00:55:17.712
We have to jump. Those
branches are only a few feet down.

546
00:55:17.731 --> 00:55:19.065
That's more like 20 feet.

547
00:55:19.149 --> 00:55:20.423
Look. Jessie. I don't
wanna burn to death.

548
00:55:20.442 --> 00:55:21.758
and I don't want to be
chopped up into pieces.

549
00:55:21.777 --> 00:55:23.653
We can do this. I'll go first.

550
00:55:25.364 --> 00:55:27.491
Chris. Hey.

551
00:56:16.040 --> 00:56:17.082
Chris!

552
00:56:17.180 --> 00:56:18.292
Chris!

553
00:56:18.751 --> 00:56:20.793
Help! Chris.

554
00:56:47.738 --> 00:56:48.738
You okay?

555
00:56:48.822 --> 00:56:50.281
Do you think they saw us?

556
00:56:50.991 --> 00:56:52.450
I don't know.

557
00:57:00.232 --> 00:57:02.358
We gotta move. Come on.

558
00:57:02.377 --> 00:57:04.504
Shit. Shit.

559
00:57:22.689 --> 00:57:24.190
Carly. come on.

560
00:58:30.424 --> 00:58:33.634
I can do this. I can
do this. I can do this.

561
00:58:34.094 --> 00:58:36.345
I can... I can do this.

562
00:59:04.708 --> 00:59:06.877
Come on. Come on.

563
00:59:27.356 --> 00:59:28.397
He's coming.

564
00:59:28.482 --> 00:59:30.775
I know. I have a plan. Come on.

565
00:59:38.825 --> 00:59:40.534
Jessie. this way.

566
01:00:04.851 --> 01:00:06.811
- Can you hold this?
- Why?

567
01:00:07.062 --> 01:00:09.523
'Cause we're gonna knock
this fucker out of the tree.

568
01:00:09.542 --> 01:00:10.901
Can you hold it?

569
01:00:11.608 --> 01:00:12.734
Yeah.

570
01:00:12.753 --> 01:00:15.237
Alright. Don't let go
until I say so. Okay?

571
01:00:15.862 --> 01:00:16.905
Where are you going?

572
01:00:16.924 --> 01:00:18.532
I'm gonna make sure
he comes this way.

573
01:00:18.699 --> 01:00:20.908
No. You can't move
as quick as I can.

574
01:00:21.106 --> 01:00:22.911
Jessie. Jessie.

575
01:00:43.878 --> 01:00:46.476
I'm right here! Come and get me!

576
01:00:51.398 --> 01:00:52.898
Where are you?

577
01:00:56.510 --> 01:00:57.844
Here I am!

578
01:01:54.836 --> 01:01:55.845
Hey!

579
01:03:36.396 --> 01:03:38.397
I'm sorry about your friends.

580
01:03:41.234 --> 01:03:45.154
Last Friday I came home. and
there's a message on my machine

581
01:03:46.198 --> 01:03:52.368
from my boyfriend. who says that
we shouldn't be together anymore.

582
01:03:55.582 --> 01:04:00.086
Within 20 minutes
of me telling Carly.

583
01:04:02.547 --> 01:04:07.256
she had Scott and
Evan and Francine

584
01:04:07.302 --> 01:04:10.596
all blowing off work this
week to take me out here.

585
01:04:12.098 --> 01:04:14.934
That's just the kind
of friends they were.

586
01:04:17.354 --> 01:04:19.146
And now they're dead.

587
01:04:28.740 --> 01:04:30.491
It's not your fault.

588
01:04:32.619 --> 01:04:33.869
It's not.

589
01:05:00.981 --> 01:05:02.440
They're here.

590
01:05:10.282 --> 01:05:11.741
No. they're not.

591
01:05:12.342 --> 01:05:13.740
You were dreaming.

592
01:05:15.120 --> 01:05:16.328
I wish.

593
01:06:02.250 --> 01:06:04.293
- How's your leg?
- It hurts.

594
01:06:04.377 --> 01:06:07.422
Which is good. If it didn't hurt...

595
01:06:07.516 --> 01:06:08.537
Road.

596
01:06:08.556 --> 01:06:10.175
- What?
- Road! Look.

597
01:06:12.052 --> 01:06:13.096
We gotta get down there.

598
01:06:13.115 --> 01:06:15.138
Take that slope right there.

599
01:06:18.683 --> 01:06:20.392
I can't believe it.

600
01:06:21.863 --> 01:06:23.688
- How are we gonna get you down?
- I'll get down...

601
01:06:26.494 --> 01:06:27.495
- Chris!
- Go!

602
01:06:27.514 --> 01:06:28.799
- Chris! Come on!
- Go!

603
01:06:28.818 --> 01:06:30.528
Chris. stop! No!

604
01:06:30.775 --> 01:06:31.779
Chris!

605
01:06:32.197 --> 01:06:33.240
Chris!

606
01:06:34.609 --> 01:06:35.816
Chris!

607
01:06:36.075 --> 01:06:37.401
Chris!

608
01:06:37.916 --> 01:06:39.412
Get off of me!

609
01:06:42.791 --> 01:06:44.124
Jessie!

610
01:06:44.417 --> 01:06:45.584
Jessie!

611
01:06:55.679 --> 01:06:56.771
Hey. stop!

612
01:06:57.622 --> 01:06:58.889
Oh. thank God.

613
01:06:59.349 --> 01:07:00.933
Are you crazy?

614
01:07:01.743 --> 01:07:03.061
- They took her. Come on. We gotta...
- Calm down.

615
01:07:03.103 --> 01:07:04.687
- Just calm down.
- We gotta move.

616
01:07:04.771 --> 01:07:06.785
Are you one of them folks who
called me from the fire tower?

617
01:07:06.804 --> 01:07:08.379
- I've been looking all over for you.
- Please. shut up and listen.

618
01:07:08.398 --> 01:07:10.750
- People are dead.
- Dead? What people?

619
01:09:28.790 --> 01:09:29.832
No!

620
01:09:34.629 --> 01:09:35.671
No.

621
01:09:42.053 --> 01:09:44.055
Help me. please.

622
01:09:45.306 --> 01:09:46.641
I'm sorry.

623
01:09:46.735 --> 01:09:48.141
I'm sorry.

624
01:09:48.434 --> 01:09:50.019
I'm sorry.

625
01:09:50.291 --> 01:09:52.742
Yeah? Can you help me?

626
01:09:53.398 --> 01:09:54.940
Please help me.

627
01:09:56.067 --> 01:09:57.276
No!

628
01:09:59.404 --> 01:10:00.487
No!

629
01:11:20.818 --> 01:11:22.636
Somebody. help me!

630
01:11:27.200 --> 01:11:28.367
No!

631
01:11:51.641 --> 01:11:52.891
Help me.

632
01:12:49.782 --> 01:12:50.889
You're okay. Come on.

633
01:12:50.908 --> 01:12:52.493
Just stay with me. You're all right.

634
01:12:52.602 --> 01:12:54.745
Come on. It's okay.

635
01:12:55.079 --> 01:12:57.539
Just keep looking at me. okay?
You're okay.

636
01:12:57.623 --> 01:12:59.041
Thank you.

637
01:12:59.675 --> 01:13:00.710
Everything's okay.

638
01:13:05.673 --> 01:13:06.716
Chris!

639
01:14:01.479 --> 01:14:02.521
Chris!

640
01:14:56.951 --> 01:14:57.952
Chris.

641
01:15:09.714 --> 01:15:11.173
Get off of me!

642
01:15:25.313 --> 01:15:26.731
Shoot them.

643
01:15:27.523 --> 01:15:29.816
I only got one shot left.

644
01:15:37.033 --> 01:15:39.901
Come on. you motherfuckers.

645
01:15:40.411 --> 01:15:41.871
Just die.
